300
00:11:50,100 --> 00:11:51,690
It's okay.

301
00:11:51,940 --> 00:11:53,660
What are we going to do,

302
00:11:54,460 --> 00:11:55,620
Miaomiao?

303
00:12:02,460 --> 00:12:10,030
[Room 3]

304
00:12:19,700 --> 00:12:20,340
Mom.

305
00:12:50,300 --> 00:12:51,300
It's hard to say.

306
00:12:52,260 --> 00:12:54,580
Some might wake up in two or three days.

307
00:12:54,990 --> 00:12:56,520
Some, in two or three years.

308
00:12:56,890 --> 00:12:57,680
And some,

309
00:12:58,330 --> 00:12:59,610
never wake up.

310
00:13:00,940 --> 00:13:01,940
And

311
00:13:02,680 --> 00:13:04,800
