312
00:13:05,630 --> 00:13:06,290
If, by some miracle,

313
00:13:06,290 --> 00:13:07,660
he wakes up,

314
00:13:08,370 --> 00:13:09,380
he won't

315
00:13:09,640 --> 00:13:11,380
be able to walk anymore.

316
00:13:12,580 --> 00:13:13,340
So,

317
00:13:14,420 --> 00:13:16,280
you need to be mentally prepared.

318
00:13:32,580 --> 00:13:33,700
They're divorced,

319
00:13:33,720 --> 00:13:35,050
