This place is full of snitches.

324
00:13:47,340 --> 00:13:49,260
When did you get back?

325
00:13:53,330 --> 00:13:54,060
Just now.

326
00:13:54,680 --> 00:13:55,900
There's no direct bus,

327
00:13:55,900 --> 00:13:57,970
