331
00:14:04,140 --> 00:14:05,340
But I didn't have fun.

332
00:14:06,020 --> 00:14:06,970
We're divorced.

333
00:14:08,140 --> 00:14:09,870
And I still can't catch a break.

334
00:14:11,300 --> 00:14:11,980
Yue,

335
00:14:12,980 --> 00:14:14,020
don't blame us.

336
00:14:14,020 --> 00:14:15,260
We didn't tell you

337
00:14:15,350 --> 00:14:17,680
because we were really worried about you.

338
00:14:19,260 --> 00:14:20,500
If we don't look out for you,

339
00:14:20,500 --> 00:14:21,780
who will?

340
00:14:24,060 --> 00:14:24,940
I get it.

341
00:14:26,260 --> 00:14:27,340
I don't blame you.

342
00:14:32,380 --> 00:14:33,890
You know, in the past,

343
00:14:34,180 --> 00:14:36,060
