358
00:17:14,380 --> 00:17:15,579
about the situation.

359
00:17:17,300 --> 00:17:17,980
Okay.

360
00:17:36,000 --> 00:17:36,840
Yang.

361
00:17:42,170 --> 00:17:43,260
