376
00:19:00,360 --> 00:19:01,280
Not yet.

377
00:19:01,410 --> 00:19:03,000
Only Lin Xiu got arrested.

378
00:19:05,220 --> 00:19:06,750
If Lin Xiu's been arrested,

379
00:19:07,670 --> 00:19:09,000
