382
00:19:15,320 --> 00:19:16,320
Did you tell them?

383
00:19:19,280 --> 00:19:21,070
How did Hu Yue find out?

384
00:19:23,060 --> 00:19:24,340
No one told her.

385
00:19:24,360 --> 00:19:25,760
She found it out herself.

386
00:19:26,340 --> 00:19:27,740
With something this big,

387
00:19:27,970 --> 00:19:29,430
