388
00:19:30,360 --> 00:19:31,640
What about Yang Tao?

389
00:19:32,130 --> 00:19:33,190
Does Yang Tao know?

390
00:19:33,650 --> 00:19:34,800
Min said that

391
00:19:35,710 --> 00:19:37,150
