392
00:19:37,820 --> 00:19:38,550
so we thought

393
00:19:38,820 --> 00:19:40,640
we'd talk it over with you.

394
00:19:41,860 --> 00:19:42,940
Don't tell him.

395
00:19:44,380 --> 00:19:45,990
Don't affect his exams.

396
00:19:48,740 --> 00:19:50,660
Also, don't tell my mom

397
00:19:50,660 --> 00:19:51,790
or brother either.

398
00:19:54,570 --> 00:19:55,710
I'll be fine lying here

399
00:19:55,710 --> 00:19:57,450
in the hospital by myself.

400
00:19:57,870 --> 00:19:59,930
I don't need anyone to take care of me.

401
00:19:59,970 --> 00:20:01,270
How can you say that?

402
00:20:03,340 --> 00:20:05,270
In your condition, you definitely

403
00:20:06,270 --> 00:20:08,000
need someone to look after you.

404
00:20:09,790 --> 00:20:11,250
Pengfei, could you help me

405
00:20:12,640 --> 00:20:14,070
ask something?

406
00:20:14,110 --> 00:20:16,260
How long do I have to stay in bed?

407
00:20:19,110 --> 00:20:19,870
Also,

408
00:20:21,100 --> 00:20:23,650
