409
00:20:23,700 --> 00:20:25,310
You fell from

410
00:20:25,340 --> 00:20:26,140
such a height;

411
00:20:27,270 --> 00:20:28,230
it's going to take time.

412
00:20:28,230 --> 00:20:30,160
You'll recover slowly, bit by bit.

413
00:20:31,150 --> 00:20:33,010
Exactly, there's no need to rush.

414
00:20:45,300 --> 00:20:46,380
Now that Yang has woken up,

415
00:20:46,380 --> 00:20:48,510
you really need to think this through.

416
00:20:49,180 --> 00:20:49,780
Yue.

417
00:20:50,480 --> 00:20:51,520
This isn't something you'll

418
00:20:51,520 --> 00:20:52,860
just deal with for a few days.

419
00:20:52,860 --> 00:20:53,420
The doctor

420
00:20:53,420 --> 00:20:55,030
already explained his condition.

421
00:20:55,030 --> 00:20:55,990
You're not thinking of

422
00:20:55,990 --> 00:20:57,990
