427
00:21:11,100 --> 00:21:12,860
The factory won't leave him unattended.

428
00:21:12,860 --> 00:21:14,900
Yeah, the company will definitely help.

429
00:21:14,900 --> 00:21:16,760
But the people the company sends,

430
00:21:16,840 --> 00:21:17,730
they'll just handle

431
00:21:17,730 --> 00:21:19,190
his meals and basic needs.

432
00:21:20,500 --> 00:21:21,460
I know Yang's temper

433
00:21:21,460 --> 00:21:22,500
too well.

434
00:21:23,480 --> 00:21:24,580
If he realizes

435
00:21:24,580 --> 00:21:26,060
he'll never stand again,

436
00:21:27,210 --> 00:21:29,180
I can't even imagine what will happen.

437
00:21:29,180 --> 00:21:30,130
We'll see.

438
00:21:30,540 --> 00:21:31,160
For now, I'll stay with him

439
00:21:31,160 --> 00:21:32,200
for a while.

440
00:21:32,230 --> 00:21:33,320
What else can I do?

441
00:22:25,400 --> 00:22:26,700
What are you doing?

442
00:22:26,700 --> 00:22:28,220
That's gotta hurt!

443
00:22:28,240 --> 00:22:29,390
It doesn't hurt.

444
00:22:31,110 --> 00:22:32,750
It's been over a month,

445
00:22:32,940 --> 00:22:34,500
