460
00:23:16,820 --> 00:23:17,420
Alright.

461
00:23:20,220 --> 00:23:20,980
Yang.

462
00:23:21,920 --> 00:23:23,180
-Don't move.
-Mr. Liu.

463
00:23:24,580 --> 00:23:25,100
Yang.

464
00:23:25,120 --> 00:23:26,340
-You are?
-Lie down. Lie down.

465
00:23:26,340 --> 00:23:26,700
Okay.

466
00:23:26,720 --> 00:23:28,050
You must be Yang's wife?

467
00:23:28,310 --> 00:23:29,110
Yes, I am.

468
00:23:29,340 --> 00:23:30,800
You've been through a lot.

469
00:23:31,830 --> 00:23:33,460
You can rest assured

470
00:23:34,140 --> 00:23:36,300
about Yang's treatment, care,

471
00:23:36,510 --> 00:23:38,510
and rehabilitation.

472
00:23:38,550 --> 00:23:40,480
We will take full responsibility.

473
00:23:40,860 --> 00:23:41,700
No. 3 Factory

474
00:23:41,770 --> 00:23:44,050
will always be your firm support.

475
00:23:44,140 --> 00:23:45,100
Thank you.

476
00:23:47,450 --> 00:23:49,500
How are you feeling lately?

477
00:23:51,220 --> 00:23:52,480
I'm doing alright now.

478
00:23:52,990 --> 00:23:53,870
Good to hear.

479
00:23:54,600 --> 00:23:55,760
Our leadership team

480
00:23:55,790 --> 00:23:57,340
heard about your heroic actions,

481
00:23:57,340 --> 00:23:59,070
and everyone was deeply moved.

482
00:23:59,140 --> 00:24:00,940
The entire staff at No. 3 Factory

483
00:24:01,040 --> 00:24:03,230
is concerned about your health.

484
00:24:03,620 --> 00:24:05,970
We're all hoping for your speedy recovery.

485
00:24:05,970 --> 00:24:07,910
Thank you, thank you for your concern.

486
00:24:07,910 --> 00:24:08,790
Yang,

487
00:24:09,140 --> 00:24:10,620
if you hadn't manually

488
00:24:10,750 --> 00:24:12,020
reduced the pressure in time,

489
00:24:12,020 --> 00:24:14,280
the consequences would have been unimaginable.

490
00:24:14,280 --> 00:24:16,390
In recognition of your bravery,

491
00:24:16,830 --> 00:24:19,950
we, on behalf of Linqi Oilfield Headquarters,

492
00:24:19,970 --> 00:24:22,840
