00:24:26,100 --> 00:24:27,980
the pain you're enduring,

496
00:24:28,170 --> 00:24:29,430
this is Linqi Oilfield

497
00:24:29,440 --> 00:24:31,320
and Factory No. 3 Factory's way

498
00:24:31,440 --> 00:24:32,640
of honoring a hero.

