504
00:24:53,840 --> 00:24:54,720
By the way, Liu,

505
00:24:55,400 --> 00:24:56,600
from today onward,

506
00:24:56,620 --> 00:24:59,190
report Yang's treatment and recovery progress

507
00:24:59,190 --> 00:25:00,190
to me regularly.

508
00:25:00,310 --> 00:25:00,840
Yes, sir.

509
00:25:00,850 --> 00:25:02,920
If you encounter any difficulties, reach out to us anytime.

510
00:25:02,920 --> 00:25:03,650
Yes, sir.

511
00:25:03,720 --> 00:25:04,320
Okay.

512
00:25:04,540 --> 00:25:05,410
Let's take a group photo

513
00:25:05,410 --> 00:25:06,450
