550
00:26:06,660 --> 00:26:07,700
Goodbye, Li Si.

551
00:26:07,760 --> 00:26:08,600
Ribs?

552
00:26:09,110 --> 00:26:09,900
How much

553
00:26:10,740 --> 00:26:11,810
