This is a hospital!

586
00:29:14,940 --> 00:29:16,270
You don't own it!

587
00:29:16,810 --> 00:29:17,650
You think just because you want me to leave,

588
00:29:17,650 --> 00:29:18,450
-I'll go?
-I don't need

589
00:29:18,450 --> 00:29:19,420
your pity!

590
00:29:19,420 --> 00:29:20,540
I'm not leaving!

591
00:29:20,560 --> 00:29:23,010
I don't need anyone's pity!

592
00:29:28,060 --> 00:29:29,180
Damn hospital.

593
00:29:30,340 --> 00:29:31,620
I don't need it!

594
00:29:56,820 --> 00:29:57,680
I don't need it!

595
00:30:00,010 --> 00:30:00,940
Throw a tantrum,

596
00:30:03,180 --> 00:30:04,220
keep going.

597
00:30:05,340 --> 00:30:07,280
Didn't you say you wanted me to leave?

598
00:30:07,280 --> 00:30:07,920
Then go.

599
00:30:07,950 --> 00:30:09,680
The door's right there—leave!

600
00:30:19,130 --> 00:30:20,050
Had enough?

601
00:30:22,700 --> 00:30:24,570
Now do you understand your situation?

602
00:30:24,570 --> 00:30:26,300
Do you have a clear picture now?

603
00:30:26,750 --> 00:30:28,410
Let me tell you, Yang Songbai,

604
00:30:29,540 --> 00:30:31,800
from now on, you're going to listen to me.

605
00:30:32,210 --> 00:30:33,710
No more tantrums.

606
00:30:34,300 --> 00:30:40,950
You all—you all lied to me.

607
00:30:51,220 --> 00:30:55,100
You all lied to me.

608
00:30:55,740 --> 00:30:56,940
Take your hands away.

609
00:31:19,350 --> 00:31:20,950
You eat what you need to heal.

610
00:31:21,020 --> 00:31:22,120
I picked out the biggest

611
00:31:22,120 --> 00:31:23,750
pig's trotters at the market.

612
00:31:23,750 --> 00:31:24,610
Come on, try it.

613
00:31:25,980 --> 00:31:27,570
I've been eating this for a week straight.

614
00:31:27,570 --> 00:31:28,260
At this rate,

615
00:31:28,260 --> 00:31:29,530
