616
00:31:29,530 --> 00:31:30,530
We're just getting started.

617
00:31:30,530 --> 00:31:31,590
Besides, what's wrong with gaining a little weight?

618
00:31:31,590 --> 00:31:33,500
Round and plump—it's a sign of good fortune!

619
00:31:33,500 --> 00:31:34,500
Attracts wealth.

620
00:31:38,770 --> 00:31:40,410
You finally got yourself a job,

621
00:31:40,410 --> 00:31:42,030
so stop coming over here all the time.

622
00:31:42,030 --> 00:31:43,290
It doesn't interfere.

623
00:31:43,420 --> 00:31:45,220
I'll leave right after you finish eating.

624
00:31:45,220 --> 00:31:46,890
Yeah, you know, that restaurant really needs me.

625
00:31:46,890 --> 00:31:48,450
They wouldn't manage without me.

626
00:31:48,450 --> 00:31:50,240
Then you'd better work hard for them.

627
00:31:50,240 --> 00:31:51,390
I am working hard!

628
00:31:52,330 --> 00:31:53,850
Do you know what a lobby manager is?

629
00:31:53,850 --> 00:31:55,700
That's the face of the restaurant!

630
00:31:55,700 --> 00:31:56,730
Xiaoshudu Restaurant

631
00:31:56,730 --> 00:31:57,550
is one of the biggest restaurants

632
00:31:57,550 --> 00:31:58,660
in the oilfield area.

633
00:31:58,660 --> 00:32:00,280
All the important people come to eat here.

634
00:32:00,280 --> 00:32:01,480
They're all leaders.

635
00:32:02,060 --> 00:32:03,740
I'm not worried about

636
00:32:03,830 --> 00:32:04,950
networking at all.

637
00:32:06,070 --> 00:32:06,900
Sounds like

638
00:32:06,930 --> 00:32:07,910
you've got it all figured out.

639
00:32:07,910 --> 00:32:09,970
Of course! You gotta plan carefully.

640
00:32:11,190 --> 00:32:12,720
How's the taste—too salty?

641
00:32:12,800 --> 00:32:14,200
The taste is fine,

642
00:32:14,690 --> 00:32:16,080
but I can't just drink the soup!

643
00:32:16,080 --> 00:32:18,080
Give me a piece of the pig's trotter!

644
00:32:18,700 --> 00:32:19,380
My bad!

645
00:32:19,930 --> 00:32:21,790
Customers' requests come first.

646
00:32:29,740 --> 00:32:30,670
Alright, make some space.

647
00:32:30,670 --> 00:32:31,310
Here.

648
00:32:35,370 --> 00:32:37,310
Since you were little, you've always loved fish.

649
00:32:37,310 --> 00:32:38,760
Your uncle said

650
00:32:39,010 --> 00:32:41,410
he made a yellow croaker just for you today.

651
00:32:43,890 --> 00:32:45,250
Here, switch it up.

652
00:32:46,140 --> 00:32:46,710
Yes. Here.

653
00:32:46,710 --> 00:32:47,310
Switch it.

654
00:32:48,860 --> 00:32:49,540
Closer.

655
00:32:49,920 --> 00:32:51,390
Now, your most important task

656
00:32:51,390 --> 00:32:52,580
is to eat well

657
00:32:52,620 --> 00:32:53,540
and sleep well,

658
00:32:53,950 --> 00:32:54,560
right?

659
00:32:55,090 --> 00:32:56,200
Your mom is in the hospital

660
00:32:56,200 --> 00:32:57,380
taking care of Yang.

661
00:32:57,690 --> 00:32:58,850
You can't make them

662
00:32:58,870 --> 00:33:00,510
worry about you on top of that.

663
00:33:00,510 --> 00:33:01,310
If you do,

664
00:33:01,340 --> 00:33:02,870
none of you will be at peace.

665
00:33:02,900 --> 00:33:05,070
Right.

666
00:33:05,840 --> 00:33:06,770
People get sick,

667
00:33:07,760 --> 00:33:08,760
When you're sick,

668
00:33:08,780 --> 00:33:10,360
you find the doctor.

669
00:33:10,660 --> 00:33:11,900
But

670
00:33:11,930 --> 00:33:12,770
it's up to the doctors to treat it.

671
00:33:12,770 --> 00:33:14,150
No one else can help with that,

672
00:33:14,150 --> 00:33:14,790
right?

673
00:33:15,110 --> 00:33:17,940
So, for the sake of your mom and Yang,

674
00:33:18,290 --> 00:33:19,550
don't make them worry.

675
00:33:19,560 --> 00:33:21,080
Take care of yourself.

676
00:33:21,940 --> 00:33:23,420
I know it's hard,

677
00:33:23,630 --> 00:33:25,470
but we have to try our best.

678
00:33:27,500 --> 00:33:29,570
Come on, eat.

679
00:33:30,150 --> 00:33:32,280
Wait for your mom and Yang to come back.

680
00:33:41,140 --> 00:33:42,030
Now, eat!

681
00:33:42,220 --> 00:33:43,060
Eat, eat!

682
00:33:43,060 --> 00:33:43,810
Eat, eat!

683
00:33:43,810 --> 00:33:44,260
Eat.

684
00:33:50,950 --> 00:33:51,590
Yaya.

685
00:33:51,980 --> 00:33:53,300
I made some ribs.

686
00:33:53,900 --> 00:33:55,820
Take them to Shanqing later, will you?

687
00:33:55,820 --> 00:33:56,360
Sure!

688
00:34:01,120 --> 00:34:02,510
Li Si, I guess you can't reach it.

689
00:34:02,510 --> 00:34:03,160
Mom.

690
00:34:04,290 --> 00:34:06,070
This amount is not bad at all.

691
00:34:06,810 --> 00:34:09,400
This family just wants a girl.

692
00:34:09,980 --> 00:34:11,780
She'll have a good life for sure.

693
00:34:12,409 --> 00:34:13,940
Can we ask for a little more?

694
00:34:14,699 --> 00:34:15,429
Brother,

695
00:34:15,940 --> 00:34:18,500
be content with what I've helped you with.

696
00:34:19,130 --> 00:34:20,530
You know how you broke

697
00:34:20,560 --> 00:34:21,510
that leg of yours.

698
00:34:21,510 --> 00:34:23,150
Shouldn't you be more careful?

699
00:34:23,150 --> 00:34:24,880
If you don't want it, forget it.

700
00:34:27,690 --> 00:34:28,750
When will they pay?

701
00:34:29,360 --> 00:34:30,650
When will you get the girl?

702
00:34:30,650 --> 00:34:32,110
In the next couple of days.

703
00:34:32,300 --> 00:34:34,830
When I see the person, I'll give you the money.

704
00:34:54,739 --> 00:34:56,210
I went early today.

705
00:34:57,470 --> 00:34:58,720
The food's too hot.

706
00:34:58,830 --> 00:34:59,820
Let's wait a bit before eating.

707
00:34:59,820 --> 00:35:02,820
Let's do your rehabilitation exercises first, okay?

708
00:35:02,860 --> 00:35:03,420
Okay.

709
00:35:20,050 --> 00:35:21,080
What are you staring at?

710
00:35:21,080 --> 00:35:23,240
What's on your mind?

711
00:35:26,810 --> 00:35:29,140
Use your hands. Put some strength into it.

712
00:35:29,240 --> 00:35:30,720
I'm telling you, Yang,

713
00:35:31,230 --> 00:35:32,460
once you're discharged and back home,

714
00:35:32,460 --> 00:35:33,990
you can't stop your rehab.

715
00:35:35,180 --> 00:35:36,340
No tantrums.

716
00:35:36,340 --> 00:35:38,140
You need to stick with it, got it?

717
00:35:40,680 --> 00:35:41,970
I forgot to tell you—

718
00:35:42,420 --> 00:35:43,210
I had Min

719
00:35:43,240 --> 00:35:44,380
move all your stuff

720
00:35:44,380 --> 00:35:45,220
from the dormitory

721
00:35:45,220 --> 00:35:46,020
back home.

722
00:35:49,160 --> 00:35:50,080
What?

723
00:35:50,650 --> 00:35:52,180
Don't want to go back there?

724
00:35:52,450 --> 00:35:53,510
Where do you want to go then?

725
00:35:53,510 --> 00:35:54,640
To your mom's place?

726
00:35:54,980 --> 00:35:56,500
Or your ex-wife's place?

727
00:35:57,460 --> 00:35:58,100
Wait—

728
00:35:59,080 --> 00:36:00,440
I'm also your ex-wife.

729
00:36:00,700 --> 00:36:01,890
Two ex-wives, huh?

730
00:36:02,620 --> 00:36:04,080
Maybe you should pick one.

731
00:36:04,210 --> 00:36:06,810
Whichever one you choose, I'll send you there.

732
00:36:14,260 --> 00:36:14,900
Hu Yue.

733
00:36:18,430 --> 00:36:19,070
You...

734
00:36:20,380 --> 00:36:21,340
What?

735
00:36:22,900 --> 00:36:23,620
Are you feeling touched

736
00:36:23,620 --> 00:36:25,750
by the way I've been taking care of you?

737
00:36:26,140 --> 00:36:27,500
Please, don't be.

738
00:36:27,500 --> 00:36:28,810
I have motives.

739
00:36:30,860 --> 00:36:32,260
I'm practical now.

740
00:36:35,290 --> 00:36:37,050
I'm after your salary,

741
00:36:37,470 --> 00:36:38,540
and your bonus.

742
00:36:38,570 --> 00:36:39,770
You got promoted too.

743
00:36:40,170 --> 00:36:40,940
When

744
00:36:40,940 --> 00:36:41,700
we were together,

745
00:36:41,700 --> 00:36:43,460
you had nothing.

746
00:36:43,480 --> 00:36:45,210
You didn't even buy me jewelry.

747
00:36:45,350 --> 00:36:46,550
Now, I'm here to claim

748
00:36:46,580 --> 00:36:47,640
what's mine—

749
00:36:48,220 --> 00:36:49,740
to make up for

750
00:36:49,770 --> 00:36:51,440
all the hardships I went through.

751
00:36:51,440 --> 00:36:52,370
Got it?

752
00:37:00,100 --> 00:37:01,720
What are you doing? Hands.

753
00:37:23,090 --> 00:37:23,750
I'm not taking care of you

754
00:37:23,750 --> 00:37:25,120
for free.

755
00:37:26,890 --> 00:37:28,650
You need to pay me wages,

756
00:37:30,130 --> 00:37:31,000
double.

757
00:37:36,150 --> 00:37:37,010
Are you hungry?

758
00:37:37,820 --> 00:37:38,500
Hungry.

759
00:37:40,270 --> 00:37:41,470
Let's eat first then.

760
00:37:59,320 --> 00:38:00,080
Coming.

761
00:38:12,330 --> 00:38:13,330
Cook me some food.

762
00:38:36,090 --> 00:38:37,350
All we have is noodles.

763
00:38:39,750 --> 00:38:40,830
Anything's fine.

764
00:38:57,100 --> 00:38:58,340
Good girl.

765
00:39:02,360 --> 00:39:03,820
What happened to your leg?

766
00:39:04,270 --> 00:39:05,360
Got bitten by a dog.

767
00:39:22,930 --> 00:39:24,660
The police came looking for me.

768
00:39:26,560 --> 00:39:27,400
They said

769
00:39:28,820 --> 00:39:30,280
Lin Xiu has been arrested.

770
00:39:36,700 --> 00:39:38,160
They even asked about you.

771
00:39:39,860 --> 00:39:41,660
I didn't tell them you came back.

772
00:39:50,780 --> 00:39:51,890
The police said

773
00:39:52,400 --> 00:39:53,880
if you turn yourself in,

774
00:39:54,250 --> 00:39:56,110
you might get a lighter sentence.

775
00:40:03,440 --> 00:40:04,570
A lighter sentence?

776
00:40:06,690 --> 00:40:08,020
Lin Xiu must have

777
00:40:08,120 --> 00:40:08,910
pinned everything on me.

778
00:40:08,910 --> 00:40:10,090
If I turn myself in,

779
00:40:12,990 --> 00:40:14,630
it's a death sentence.

780
00:40:15,340 --> 00:40:17,700
No, they said

781
00:40:17,730 --> 00:40:19,010
this is just fraud.

782
00:40:19,180 --> 00:40:21,240
-If you turn yourself in...
-Shut up.

783
00:40:27,220 --> 00:40:29,020
I'll leave once I finish eating.

784
00:40:30,430 --> 00:40:31,360
Pack a couple of

785
00:40:31,390 --> 00:40:32,660
Zi's clothes.

786
00:40:35,840 --> 00:40:37,160
I'm taking her with me.

787
00:40:41,000 --> 00:40:42,400
Where are you taking her?

788
00:40:43,070 --> 00:40:44,690
I'll find her a rich family.

789
00:40:45,010 --> 00:40:46,480
Zi'll have a good life.

790
00:40:56,040 --> 00:40:57,280
You're selling Zi?

791
00:41:01,520 --> 00:41:03,320
That family will treat her well.

792
00:41:06,290 --> 00:41:08,490
And she won't be a burden to you anymore.

793
00:41:08,510 --> 00:41:09,310
It's perfect.

794
00:41:09,890 --> 00:41:11,220
She's not a burden to me.

795
00:41:12,070 --> 00:41:13,270
I can take care of her.

796
00:41:14,420 --> 00:41:15,620
Dad, I'm begging you,

797
00:41:16,110 --> 00:41:17,230
don't sell her.

798
00:41:18,300 --> 00:41:20,010
She's your own daughter.

799
00:41:20,850 --> 00:41:22,310
What good is being related

800
00:41:24,070 --> 00:41:25,400
if I can't even survive?

801
00:41:47,170 --> 00:41:47,920
Help!

802
00:41:55,940 --> 00:41:57,470
What are you screaming for?

803
00:41:58,620 --> 00:42:00,220
What are you shouting about?

804
00:42:02,040 --> 00:42:03,900
Are you trying to call the police?

805
00:42:30,870 --> 00:42:33,200
Yuan Shanqing, call the police, quickly!

806
00:42:36,930 --> 00:42:39,220
[In Operation]

807
00:42:37,080 --> 00:42:38,160
That early summer,

808
00:42:38,530 --> 00:42:40,390
every day was filled with danger.

809
00:42:40,900 --> 00:42:42,630
We were all on edge,

810
00:42:43,650 --> 00:42:45,780
not knowing when the storm would stop,

811
00:42:45,930 --> 00:42:46,620
not knowing

812
00:42:46,620 --> 00:42:48,150
if the floods would return,

813
00:42:48,380 --> 00:42:50,540
not knowing if our parents were safe,

814
00:42:51,060 --> 00:42:53,590
not knowing that disaster had already struck.

815
00:42:53,590 --> 00:42:55,620
Our home was protected,

816
00:42:56,290 --> 00:42:57,650
but our youth

817
00:42:58,450 --> 00:42:59,970
met its disaster.

818
00:43:00,420 --> 00:43:02,180
We all remember that summer.

819
00:43:02,840 --> 00:43:04,550
It changed our lives forever.
